31/*%
32 * Bit positions in the dns_peer_t structure flags field
33 */
34#define BOGUS_BIT 0
35#define SERVER_TRANSFER_FORMAT_BIT 1
36#define TRANSFERS_BIT 2
37#define PROVIDE_IXFR_BIT 3
38#define REQUEST_IXFR_BIT 4
39#define SUPPORT_EDNS_BIT 5
40#define SERVER_UDPSIZE_BIT 6
41#define SERVER_MAXUDP_BIT 7
42#define REQUEST_NSID_BIT 8
43#define SEND_COOKIE_BIT 9
44#define NOTIFY_DSCP_BIT 10
45#define TRANSFER_DSCP_BIT 11
46#define QUERY_DSCP_BIT 12
47#define REQUEST_EXPIRE_BIT 13
48#define EDNS_VERSION_BIT 14
49#define FORCE_TCP_BIT 15
50#define SERVER_PADDING_BIT 16
51#define REQUEST_TCP_KEEPALIVE_BIT 17

53static void
54peerlist_delete(dns_peerlist_t **list);
55
56static void
57peer_delete(dns_peer_t **peer);

59isc_result_t
60dns_peerlist_new(isc_mem_t *mem, dns_peerlist_t **list) {
61 dns_peerlist_t *l;
62
63 REQUIRE(list != NULL);
64
65 l = isc_mem_get(mem, sizeof(*l));
66 if (l == NULL)
67 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
68
69 ISC_LIST_INIT(l->elements);
70 l->mem = mem;
71 l->refs = 1;
72 l->magic = DNS_PEERLIST_MAGIC;
73
74 *list = l;
75
76 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
77}
78
79void
80dns_peerlist_attach(dns_peerlist_t *source, dns_peerlist_t **target) {
81 REQUIRE(DNS_PEERLIST_VALID(source));
82 REQUIRE(target != NULL);
83 REQUIRE(*target == NULL);
84
85 source->refs++;
86
87 ENSURE(source->refs != 0xffffffffU);
88
89 *target = source;
90}
91
92void
93dns_peerlist_detach(dns_peerlist_t **list) {
94 dns_peerlist_t *plist;
95
96 REQUIRE(list != NULL);
97 REQUIRE(*list != NULL);
98 REQUIRE(DNS_PEERLIST_VALID(*list));
99
100 plist = *list;
101 *list = NULL;
102
103 REQUIRE(plist->refs > 0);
104
105 plist->refs--;
106
107 if (plist->refs == 0)
108 peerlist_delete(&plist);
109}
110
111static void
112peerlist_delete(dns_peerlist_t **list) {
113 dns_peerlist_t *l;
114 dns_peer_t *server, *stmp;
115
116 REQUIRE(list != NULL);
117 REQUIRE(DNS_PEERLIST_VALID(*list));
118
119 l = *list;
120
121 REQUIRE(l->refs == 0);
122
123 server = ISC_LIST_HEAD(l->elements);
124 while (server != NULL) {
125 stmp = ISC_LIST_NEXT(server, next);
126 ISC_LIST_UNLINK(l->elements, server, next);
127 dns_peer_detach(&server);
128 server = stmp;
129 }
130
131 l->magic = 0;
132 isc_mem_put(l->mem, l, sizeof(*l));
133
134 *list = NULL;
135}
136
137void
138dns_peerlist_addpeer(dns_peerlist_t *peers, dns_peer_t *peer) {
139 dns_peer_t *p = NULL;
140
141 dns_peer_attach(peer, &p);
142
143 /*
144 * More specifics to front of list.
145 */
146 for (p = ISC_LIST_HEAD(peers->elements);
147 p != NULL;
148 p = ISC_LIST_NEXT(p, next))
149 if (p->prefixlen < peer->prefixlen)
150 break;
151
152 if (p != NULL)
153 ISC_LIST_INSERTBEFORE(peers->elements, p, peer, next);
154 else
155 ISC_LIST_APPEND(peers->elements, peer, next);
156
157}
158
159isc_result_t
160dns_peerlist_peerbyaddr(dns_peerlist_t *servers, const isc_netaddr_t *addr,
161 dns_peer_t **retval)
162{
163 dns_peer_t *server;
164 isc_result_t res;
165
166 REQUIRE(retval != NULL);
167 REQUIRE(DNS_PEERLIST_VALID(servers));
168
169 server = ISC_LIST_HEAD(servers->elements);
170 while (server != NULL) {
171 if (isc_netaddr_eqprefix(addr, &server->address,
172 server->prefixlen))
173 break;
174
175 server = ISC_LIST_NEXT(server, next);
176 }
177
178 if (server != NULL) {
179 *retval = server;
180 res = ISC_R_SUCCESS;
181 } else {
182 res = ISC_R_NOTFOUND;
183 }
184
185 return (res);
186}

190isc_result_t
191dns_peerlist_currpeer(dns_peerlist_t *peers, dns_peer_t **retval) {
192 dns_peer_t *p = NULL;
193
194 p = ISC_LIST_TAIL(peers->elements);
195
196 dns_peer_attach(p, retval);
197
198 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
199}

201isc_result_t
202dns_peer_new(isc_mem_t *mem, const isc_netaddr_t *addr, dns_peer_t **peerptr) {
203 unsigned int prefixlen = 0;
204
205 REQUIRE(peerptr != NULL);
206 switch(addr->family) {
207 case AF_INET:
208 prefixlen = 32;
209 break;
210 case AF_INET6:
211 prefixlen = 128;
212 break;
213 default:
214 INSIST(0);
215 ISC_UNREACHABLE();
216 }
217
218 return (dns_peer_newprefix(mem, addr, prefixlen, peerptr));
219}
220
221isc_result_t
222dns_peer_newprefix(isc_mem_t *mem, const isc_netaddr_t *addr,
223 unsigned int prefixlen, dns_peer_t **peerptr)
224{
225 dns_peer_t *peer;
226
227 REQUIRE(peerptr != NULL);
228
229 peer = isc_mem_get(mem, sizeof(*peer));
230 if (peer == NULL)
231 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
232
233 peer->magic = DNS_PEER_MAGIC;
234 peer->address = *addr;
235 peer->prefixlen = prefixlen;
236 peer->mem = mem;
237 peer->bogus = false;
238 peer->transfer_format = dns_one_answer;
239 peer->transfers = 0;
240 peer->request_ixfr = false;
241 peer->provide_ixfr = false;
242 peer->key = NULL;
243 peer->refs = 1;
244 peer->transfer_source = NULL;
245 peer->notify_source = NULL;
246 peer->query_source = NULL;
247
248 memset(&peer->bitflags, 0x0, sizeof(peer->bitflags));
249
250 ISC_LINK_INIT(peer, next);
251
252 *peerptr = peer;
253
254 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
255}

257void
258dns_peer_attach(dns_peer_t *source, dns_peer_t **target) {
259 REQUIRE(DNS_PEER_VALID(source));
260 REQUIRE(target != NULL);
261 REQUIRE(*target == NULL);
262
263 source->refs++;
264
265 ENSURE(source->refs != 0xffffffffU);
266
267 *target = source;
268}
269
270void
271dns_peer_detach(dns_peer_t **peer) {
272 dns_peer_t *p;
273
274 REQUIRE(peer != NULL);
275 REQUIRE(*peer != NULL);
276 REQUIRE(DNS_PEER_VALID(*peer));
277
278 p = *peer;
279
280 REQUIRE(p->refs > 0);
281
282 *peer = NULL;
283 p->refs--;
284
285 if (p->refs == 0)
286 peer_delete(&p);
287}
288
289static void
290peer_delete(dns_peer_t **peer) {
291 dns_peer_t *p;
292 isc_mem_t *mem;
293
294 REQUIRE(peer != NULL);
295 REQUIRE(DNS_PEER_VALID(*peer));
296
297 p = *peer;
298
299 REQUIRE(p->refs == 0);
300
301 mem = p->mem;
302 p->mem = NULL;
303 p->magic = 0;
304
305 if (p->key != NULL) {
306 dns_name_free(p->key, mem);
307 isc_mem_put(mem, p->key, sizeof(dns_name_t));
308 }
309
310 if (p->query_source != NULL)
311 isc_mem_put(mem, p->query_source, sizeof(*p->query_source));
312
313 if (p->notify_source != NULL)
314 isc_mem_put(mem, p->notify_source, sizeof(*p->notify_source));
315
316 if (p->transfer_source != NULL)
317 isc_mem_put(mem, p->transfer_source,
318 sizeof(*p->transfer_source));
319
320 isc_mem_put(mem, p, sizeof(*p));
321
322 *peer = NULL;
323}

327 bool existed;
328
329 REQUIRE(DNS_PEER_VALID(peer));
330

333 peer->bogus = newval;
334 DNS_BIT_SET(BOGUS_BIT, &peer->bitflags);
335
336 return (existed ? ISC_R_EXISTS : ISC_R_SUCCESS);
337}

628isc_result_t
629dns_peer_setkey(dns_peer_t *peer, dns_name_t **keyval) {
630 bool exists = false;
631
632 if (peer->key != NULL) {
633 dns_name_free(peer->key, peer->mem);
634 isc_mem_put(peer->mem, peer->key, sizeof(dns_name_t));
635 exists = true;
636 }
637
638 peer->key = *keyval;
639 *keyval = NULL;
640
641 return (exists ? ISC_R_EXISTS : ISC_R_SUCCESS);
642}
643
644isc_result_t
645dns_peer_setkeybycharp(dns_peer_t *peer, const char *keyval) {
646 isc_buffer_t b;
647 dns_fixedname_t fname;
648 dns_name_t *name;
649 isc_result_t result;
650
651 dns_fixedname_init(&fname);
652 isc_buffer_constinit(&b, keyval, strlen(keyval));
653 isc_buffer_add(&b, strlen(keyval));
654 result = dns_name_fromtext(dns_fixedname_name(&fname), &b,
655 dns_rootname, 0, NULL);
656 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
657 return (result);
658
659 name = isc_mem_get(peer->mem, sizeof(dns_name_t));
660 if (name == NULL)
661 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
662
663 dns_name_init(name, NULL);
664 result = dns_name_dup(dns_fixedname_name(&fname), peer->mem, name);
665 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS) {
666 isc_mem_put(peer->mem, name, sizeof(dns_name_t));
667 return (result);
668 }
669
670 result = dns_peer_setkey(peer, &name);
671 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
672 isc_mem_put(peer->mem, name, sizeof(dns_name_t));
673
674 return (result);
675}

677isc_result_t
678dns_peer_settransfersource(dns_peer_t *peer,
679 const isc_sockaddr_t *transfer_source)
680{
681 REQUIRE(DNS_PEER_VALID(peer));
682
683 if (peer->transfer_source != NULL) {
684 isc_mem_put(peer->mem, peer->transfer_source,
685 sizeof(*peer->transfer_source));
686 peer->transfer_source = NULL;
687 }
688 if (transfer_source != NULL) {
689 peer->transfer_source = isc_mem_get(peer->mem,
690 sizeof(*peer->transfer_source));
691 if (peer->transfer_source == NULL)
692 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
693
694 *peer->transfer_source = *transfer_source;
695 }
696 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
697}

743isc_result_t
744dns_peer_setquerysource(dns_peer_t *peer, const isc_sockaddr_t *query_source) {
745 REQUIRE(DNS_PEER_VALID(peer));
746
747 if (peer->query_source != NULL) {
748 isc_mem_put(peer->mem, peer->query_source,
749 sizeof(*peer->query_source));
750 peer->query_source = NULL;
751 }
752 if (query_source != NULL) {
753 peer->query_source = isc_mem_get(peer->mem,
754 sizeof(*peer->query_source));
755 if (peer->query_source == NULL)
756 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
757
758 *peer->query_source = *query_source;
759 }
760 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
761}

764dns_peer_getquerysource(dns_peer_t *peer, isc_sockaddr_t *query_source) {
765 REQUIRE(DNS_PEER_VALID(peer));
766 REQUIRE(query_source != NULL);
767
768 if (peer->query_source == NULL)
769 return (ISC_R_NOTFOUND);
770 *query_source = *peer->query_source;
771 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
772}

831dns_peer_setpadding(dns_peer_t *peer, uint16_t padding) {
832 bool existed;
833
834 REQUIRE(DNS_PEER_VALID(peer));
835
836 existed = DNS_BIT_CHECK(SERVER_PADDING_BIT, &peer->bitflags);
837
838 if (padding > 512)
839 padding = 512;
840 peer->padding = padding;
841 DNS_BIT_SET(SERVER_PADDING_BIT, &peer->bitflags);
842
843 return (existed ? ISC_R_EXISTS : ISC_R_SUCCESS);
844}
